  "body": "I want to get the height of max block from other peer. How could I achieve that?\r\n\r\nFrom this website [Ethereum Wire Protocol](https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/Ethereum-Wire-Protocol), I realize some knowledge about how peers comunicate with other peers. But it seems like that peers synchronized by Total Difficulty(TD) & hash of their best block. So I can't get the base height.\r\n\r\nSo how could I get the base height? Thanks for reading it.",
